(734, 'IE', 'Closed', '2024-07-15', '3008', 'IE-2024071504', 'Partial closing of category 2. of NCR 49 & 50 (Deficiency in field core extracted and tested for UCS', '?The corrective action report on NCR 49 and 50, submitted by the Project Company, was reviewed by the IE.\n?Consent for the corrective action was taken from the PD (RHD).\n?Corrective action addressed the thickness of the layer, observed between 180 mm to 192 mm instead of the designed 180 mm, and the UCS strength observed between 5.85 Mpa to 7.97 Mpa, complying with the pavement design criteria of 5 Mpa.\n?NCR for Category 2 of NCR 49 and 50 for Km 23+000 to Km 23+430 (RHS) is considered closed.\nThis was shared with JV via email on July 16, 2024.', 'https://docs.qq.com/doc/DQ2JJeFVRUXJ3dWlq', 'Sent', 0, 0, 0, 0, 18, NULL, NULL),
