(740, 'IE', 'Closed', '2024-07-27', '3016', 'IE-2024072707', 'Closure of Site Instruction No.22 on use of broken blocks,not maintaining horizontal and vertical barrierr both side at the RE wall from Km 15+970 to Km 16+130 TR-LHS and Km 15+850 to Km 16+290 TR-RHS\n', '?The Highway Engineer reviewed the documents and corrective actions submitted by the Project Company for issues related to broken blocks, horizontal and vertical alignment, and safety barriers.\n?Broken and drilling blocks have been removed and replaced with regular shape blocks at a defective location.\n?The horizontal and vertical alignment has been verified and found to be compliant with the records, except for verticality, which does not meet technical specifications.\n?Site Instruction No. 22 can only be closed if the Project Company takes full liability for any failures due to the mentioned conditions.\n?The related documents have been attached for records and further necessary action.', 'https://docs.qq.com/doc/DQ2lmQ0dibkZhd05N', 'Processing', 1, 0, 0, 0, 18, NULL, NULL),
